/.lake
.DS_Store
# `.axiomdata/` is per-clone machine-generated state and stays untracked —
# except `files/A/.gitkeep`, tracked so the `Env` lib's glob directory
# exists in a fresh clone (a bare `lake build` errors on a missing glob
# directory; see lakefile.lean). The leading `!.axiomdata/` un-ignores the
# directory itself so the re-includes below also work when this template
# lives inside the monorepo, whose root .gitignore excludes `.axiomdata`.
!.axiomdata/
.axiomdata/*
!.axiomdata/files/
.axiomdata/files/*
!.axiomdata/files/A/
.axiomdata/files/A/*
!.axiomdata/files/A/.gitkeep
